{"word":"εἴπερ","slug":"εἴπερ","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n31159\" key=\"ei)/per\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">εἴπερ</orth> or <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">εἴ περ</orth>, strengthd. for <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">εἰ</foreign>, <sense id=\"n31159.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">if really, if indeed</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:3:25\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.25</biblScope></bibl>, etc.; esp. <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">even if, even though</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:7:117\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.117</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:1:167\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.167</biblScope></bibl>, etc.; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">εἴ. καί</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:9:35\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">9.35</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">εἴ. τε</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:10:225\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">10.225</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">εἴ. γε</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg006.perseus-grc1:198\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.\">A.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ch.\">Ch.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">198</biblScope></bibl></cit>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg022:312a\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Prt.\">Prt.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">312a</biblScope></bibl>, etc.; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">εἴ. γε δή</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg006.perseus-grc1:182c\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Tht.\">Tht.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">182c</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; with words between, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">εἴ. γάρ τε χόλον γε</foreign>. . <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:81\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.81</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">εἴπερ ἔσται γε</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg005.perseus-grc1:1249\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.\">A.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ag.\">Ag.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1249</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg008.perseus-grc1:275e\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Plt.\">Plt.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">275e</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">καλῶς, εἴπερ ποτέ, ἔχει</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0003.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:20\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.20</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">εἴπερ ἄρα</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg2003.tlg001:7:216b\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Jul.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Or.\">Or.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.216b</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n31159.1\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> in <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Att.\">Att.</a></gram> </gramGrp> and Trag. to imply that the supposition agrees with the fact, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">if as is the fact, since</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0003.tlg001.perseus-grc1:6:14\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.14</biblScope></bibl>, etc.; but with <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ impf.\">impf.</a></tns> it implies that it is contrary to the fact, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">εἴπερ ἦν πέλας</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">if</tr_> I had been (but I was not), <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg005.perseus-grc1:312\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ S.\">S.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ El.\">El.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">312</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg005.perseus-grc1:604\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">604</biblScope> </bibl>; also <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">εἴ. ἐκτελεῖς ἅπερ λέγεις</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">if only</tr_> you will keep your word, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">Ichn.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">48</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"III\" id=\"n31159.2\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> with an ellipse, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">if you must</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg003.perseus-grc1:227\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Nu.\">Nu.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">227</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀλλ᾽ εἴ.</foreign> but <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">if so</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg009:150b\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Prm.\">Prm.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">150b</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg010.perseus-grc1:1101a:12\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arist.\">Arist.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ EN\">EN</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1101a12</biblScope> </bibl>; cf. <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">εἰ</quote_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ B.\">B.</a></author> </bibl> </cit> VII.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}